{"tid":1230923,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《六月港殤奠禮需知》","createTime":"2019-06-16T10:43:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T10:50:22.000Z","uid":65299,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8feb3276bd3600ce5b9d01fea9f7dad13993444d","tid":1230923,"uid":65299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T10:43:01.000Z","msg":"《六月港殤奠禮需知》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/juneforstfuneral\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjuneforstfuneral&d=p84ZIGfbRlzA5dgw%2Bb26WEB1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=2bc95bc5\" target=\"_blank\">t.me/juneforstfuneral</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「人生自古誰無死， 留取丹心照汗青」<br />\n講出嚟好容易，做起嚟好撚難。<br />\n但一路走來，無數義士，前赴後繼為香港未來而犧牲。<br />\n命途多舛，尋晚更出現一位以死相諫嘅烈士。<br />\n<br />\n烈士絕不能枉死，我哋六十位大學生，<br />\n希望為您提供第一手陰間道路實況，提防牛鬼蛇神，<br />\n畀您喺外有蛇神，內有奸佞嘅環境，<br />\n好好安心立命，悼念死者。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n面對自九號起幾何級倍增嘅白色恐怖，<br />\n及社會不斷傳來嘅噩耗。<br />\n有人灰心、悲傷、惶恐，但痛哭過後，<br />\n請您將所有淚水同悲痛，<br />\n化成對準政權嘅矛頭，用行動去傳承烈士嘅遺志。<br />\n<br />\n如果，您自問無「慷慨就義，捨身成仁」嘅勇氣；<br />\n亦請您堅持香港人獨有嘅骨氣。<br />\n<br />\n請大家懷憂壯志；<br />\n終點未至，未可中止。<br />\n自己香港，自己救。"},{"pid":"7d6bd851c3361e3844c3eb18f007e714ca8b4648","tid":1230923,"uid":65299,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T10:43:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://t.me/juneforstfuneral\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjuneforstfuneral&d=p84ZIGfbRlzA5dgw%2Bb26WEB1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=2bc95bc5\" target=\"_blank\">t.me/juneforstfuneral</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfc8f9f0f0809606ff97e20f68dcdbe77ef353ad","tid":1230923,"uid":65299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d6bd851c3361e3844c3eb18f007e714ca8b4648","tid":1230923,"uid":65299,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T10:43:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://t.me/juneforstfuneral\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjuneforstfuneral&d=p84ZIGfbRlzA5dgw%2Bb26WEB1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=2bc95bc5\" target=\"_blank\">t.me/juneforstfuneral</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T10:46:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://t.me/juneforstfuneral\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjuneforstfuneral&d=p84ZIGfbRlzA5dgw%2Bb26WEB1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=2bc95bc5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/juneforstfuneral</a>"},{"pid":"e368d7343e8ecf64c381cfe651280abdc3f651a4","tid":1230923,"uid":148987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T10:50:22.000Z","msg":"點睇去佔禮賓府？"}]}